{"tid":1615941,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我哋【良心經濟圈\b】要打經濟戰！唔好再科金俾藍店打自己人，全部同我入黎！","createTime":"2019-10-03T08:55:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T03:02:46.000Z","uid":301438,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e0891d5e274a35c1dee889ca716781995ff9901a","tid":1615941,"uid":301438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:55:14.000Z","msg":"我哋喺<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">良心經濟圈🌏</span><br />\n<br />\n而家社會上有好多熱心市民💪🏼以現金券嘅方式幫助前線年青人🧒🏻👦🏼，但而家現金券多數都係連鎖企業M記什至係藍店劵，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">變相係科金俾藍店打自己人🔪😱！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地嘅目標就係協助良心店💛出現金券/代用劵同幫手宣傳✍🏼，等父母唔再需要買藍店劵，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>改為買黃店券代替！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n更長遠嘅目標喺，我地要團結👫👬👭良心經濟體，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">將良心店個餅做大</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">同可以請番前線年青人</span></span>，同時拒絕再幫襯藍店🙅🏻&zwj;♀️同請藍人🙅🏼&zwj;♂️，從而逐步擴大整個良心經濟鏈🔗。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">詳情：</span></strong></span><br />\n🔸現金券會係商戶同持劵者既交易，我地既角色只係幫手設計草擬張現金券同宣傳。<br />\n🔸如果商戶已有現金劵設計會用番商戶既設計，如果無我地先會幫手設計。<br />\n🔸現金劵既金額同使用條款會由商戶自行決定，我地只係協助同宣傳。<br />\n🔸初步會先出實物劵，長遠計劃會係出電子劵。<br />\n<br />\n我哋現時已有商戶願意加入或積極籌備發行現金劵當中，同時我地都好需要各方面持相同理念嘅手足加入：<br />\n宣傳<br />\n&bull; 撰稿員 多名<br />\n&bull; 繪圖員 多名<br />\n&bull; 小編 （TG, FB, IG) 多名<br />\n<br />\n&bull; 商戶開發員  多名<br />\n聯絡各良心店<br />\n<br />\n&bull; 文書 多名<br />\n負責整理database 未聯絡｜聯絡中｜整作中 list <br />\n<br />\n&bull; Developer 1名<br />\n識應用Payment Platform<br />\n<br />\n👇🏼請加入我地join &amp; follow <span style=\"font-size: large;\">良心經濟圈</span>🙆🏻&zwj;♀️🙆🏼&zwj;♂️：<br />\nTg channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hkeconcircle\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkeconcircle&d=2%2FeNT3TbtuwIHwt2a%2FmQGOaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=0d5e0d08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkeconcircle</a><br />\n<br />\n#良心經濟圈🌏 #招人"},{"pid":"b14196c962f5416943a2fdbde48034e1b392191f","tid":1615941,"uid":183693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:04:14.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你唔係仲想課金比藍絲食劵比仔女用呀？有得揀緊係撐自己友<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bdd09f404395f6c00b247e2a249cae67650a3f3","tid":1615941,"uid":27963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:05:02.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一齊做大香港既良心經濟圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e458dd4f78c3414d234d4c64a4bf98b48de2702","tid":1615941,"uid":316980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:06:19.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n見到咁多人仲買M記贖罪券真係好無奈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fec96787bcbd81ab535561a7e874bf59b254cdf","tid":1615941,"uid":171762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:06:58.000Z","msg":"推 推 推"},{"pid":"c6c249b75282dd1bd3a7e690c5112c548cb33f31","tid":1615941,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:07:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會唔會開喺時事台？"},{"pid":"d5af662bec0af2dde04d838a48463a3da3054c1f","tid":1615941,"uid":301438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e458dd4f78c3414d234d4c64a4bf98b48de2702","tid":1615941,"uid":316980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:06:19.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n見到咁多人仲買M記贖罪券真係好無奈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:08:07.000Z","msg":"其實係架，唉，"},{"pid":"f05233259b7bb6fd8e6840bde9ccd82c320eb595","tid":1615941,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT